    <a class="pub-item anim" data-anim href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/30054602/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><div class="pub-dot"></div><div class="pub-text">Assessment of late mortality risk after allogeneic blood or marrow transplantation performed in childhood<span class="pub-meta">JAMA Oncology, 2018</span></div><svg class="pub-link-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a>
